charges.charge_disposition: Defendant is sentenced to time served; one (1) year supervised release, unsupervised if deported; no fine; $100 special assessment; and other conditions as set forth.

charges.charge_description: 8:1326A.F-the defendant, a citizen and national of Mexico who was ordered removed and then physically removed from the United States on or about [1/2/07], and [2/2/07], knowingly and unlawfully re-entered the United States without first having obtained the consent of the Attorney General, or his successor, the Secretary of the Department of Homeland Security when he was found in the Western District of New York on 3/31/11
